                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-667-18550611 t18550611-667-punishment-74"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Wightman.</hi>
